# Implementation Plan - Aarogya360 Multi-Tenant Database Layer

This plan outlines the design and implementation of the database models (SQLAlchemy), data schemas (Pydantic), and tenant isolation middleware/dependency injection using FastAPI.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Multi-Tenancy Strategy**: We will implement **column-based multi-tenancy** (shared database, shared schema) using the `clinic_id` column as the tenant discriminator, since almost all entities in the schema explicitly reference `clinic_id`.
> - **Tenant Isolation**: We will provide a FastAPI dependency `get_current_tenant_id` and a multi-tenant DB session wrapper/filter to ensure that queries are always scoped to the active tenant clinic.
> - **SQL Injection Prevention**: All queries will use SQLAlchemy ORM or parameterized SQLAlchemy query constructors. Raw SQL queries will be strictly avoided.

